# Notion API Configuration / Notion API 設定

# Get your integration token from: https://www.notion.so/my-integrations

# 請到以下網址建立 Integration 並取得 Token：https://www.notion.so/my-integrations

NOTION_TOKEN=secret_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Parent Page ID (files will be created as subpages of this page)

# 父頁面 ID（檔案將建立為此頁面的子頁面）

# Extract from Notion page URL, format: xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx

# 從 Notion 頁面 URL 中取得，格式：xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx

# ✅ Correct: 25588e4a-c48d-8088-8719-d2671146a7f8 (UUID format)

# ✅ 正確：25588e4a-c48d-8088-8719-d2671146a7f8 (UUID格式)

# ❌ Wrong: Projects-25688e4ac48d80e88719d2671146a7f8 (with prefix)

# ❌ 錯誤：Projects-25688e4ac48d80e88719d2671146a7f8 (含前綴)

PARENT_PAGE_ID=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Project root directory path / 專案根目錄路徑

# Default is current directory, you can specify other paths

# 預設為當前目錄，可以指定其他路徑

PROJECT_ROOT=.

# Optional Settings - Uncomment and configure if needed

# 可選設定 - 如果需要的話可以取消註解並設定

# Maximum file content length (Notion API limit)

# 最大檔案內容長度（Notion API 限制）

# MAX_CONTENT_LENGTH=100000

# Cache file name / 快取檔案名稱

# CACHE_FILE=.notion_sync_cache.json

# Example Configuration / 範例設定：

# NOTION_TOKEN=secret_1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef12345678901234567890

# PARENT_PAGE_ID=12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789abc

# PROJECT_ROOT=./my-project